descriptionHtml:
[b]Description:[/b]
After hours of trying to get a good FXAA preset, I finally managed to achieve this. These settings make Skyrim have a lot more color and look a lot more like Oblivion. Skyrim will no longer look like a gray blob anymore. Look at the screenshots for a comparison.

[b]Requirements:[/b] 
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/131]FXAA Post Process Injector[/url]

[b]Installation:[/b]
Place the folder in your Skyrim folder (not Skyrim/data) and override all files if it asks.
author: knightspk2
